A comparison of Luminex xTAG® Gastrointestinal Pathogen Panel (xTAG GPP) and routine tests for the detection of enteropathogens circulating in Southern China. To investigate whether Luminex xTAG® Gastrointestinal Pathogen Panel (xTAG GPP) is applicable for the diagnosis of diarrhea and surveillance of enteropathogens circulating in Southern China, 290 stool samples were tested for 15 kinds of enteropathogens using xTAG GPP and compared to the results from the routine tests, including culture immunochromatography